091F8A44.Line13.6DE47: Our meeting is no coincidence. I came here to help.

27FD9937.Line7.6DE47: A stronger man would have refused Vhenard’s bribe. Neyrelle…

3D087D48.Line17.6DE47: It is so dark. I have repented. Do you think I was too late?

47AEBA84.Line31.6DE47: I have done all that was asked. The pain is gone now. This was a just punishment.

5B6CE5A3.Line21.6DE47: Yes…yes…I see it now. They have come.

7337041C.Line19.BAE4: No. Not too late. The Light has come to carry you home. Do you not see it, friend?

A31403C6.Line15.6DE47: Will you give this to her, for me? I should never have taken it.
